hrough any particular area, such as a wind turbine facility in autumn, are likely to have originated from a broad expanse of summering grounds from which they have traveled in no recognizable order. Better characterizing migration patterns and wintering behaviors of hoary bats sheds light on the evolution of migration and provides context for conserving these migrants.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Cryan, Paul M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stricker, Craig A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wunder, Michael B.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d9094d5bbca4e3d90e110835caec4f17", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/bbb2009ac81e4b5722a1fee52c051864fb16ff0f160d90c006eb61b2f25eb70b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/KMIPT22H", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/KMIPT22H", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/715848fefcfa1e108bced550c6fd26c2!/b314044-316512", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": "602-616", "title": "Ecological Applications", "volume": "24"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d9094d5bbca4e3d90e110835caec4f17"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:KMIPT